snippet.title: Crystalfall Gameplay Trailer - Wishlist Now on Steam - Open Beta December 13th
snippet.description:
Choose your class and embark on a quest through a world devastated by a mysterious asteroid, filled with steampunk enemies and epic loot. Crystalfall is an upcoming hack 'n’ slash Action RPG with randomized dungeons, theorycrafting and lootable skills.

Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2574970/Crystalfall/ 

Join thousands of other ARPG players eager for steampunk action madness in the Open Beta of Crystalfall coming December 13th 2024! 🔥 

Follow us on our social media channels for more news and highlights!
